Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}很啰嗦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}现在是上课时间
